 ng\\u1eef ph\\u00e1p v\\u00e0 t\\u1eeb v\\u1ef1ng quan tr\\u1ecdng m\\u00e0 th\\u01b0\\u1eddng xuy\\u00ean xu\\u1ea5t hi\\u1ec7n trong b\\u00e0i thi IELTS nh\\u01b0 sau:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul dir=\\\"ltr\\\">\\r\\n <li>- Ng\\u1eef ph\\u00e1p: 5 th\\u00ec c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n (hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1ea1i \\u0111\\u01a1n, hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1ea1i ti\\u1ebfp di\\u1ec5n, hi\\u1ec7n t\\u1ea1i ho\\u00e0n th\\u00e0nh, qu\\u00e1 kh\\u1ee9 \\u0111\\u01a1n, t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng lai \\u0111\\u01a1n)<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>- T\\u1eeb lo\\u1ea1i (danh - \\u0111\\u1ed9ng - t\\u00ednh - tr\\u1ea1ng), S-V agreement (s\\u1ef1 ho\\u00e0 h\\u1ee3p ch\\u1ee7 ng\\u1eef - \\u0111\\u1ed9ng t\\u1eeb), M\\u1ec7nh \\u0111\\u1ec1 quan h\\u1ec7\\u2026<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>- T\\u1eeb v\\u1ef1ng: Family, Friends, Accommodation, Hobby, Music, Art, Internet, Reading, Travel, Culture, The World...<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p dir=\\\"ltr\\\">B\\u1ea1n c\\u00f3 th\\u1ec3 tham kh\\u1ea3o nh\\u1eefng t\\u00e0i li\\u1ec7u sau \\u0111\\u1ec3 c\\u1ea3i thi\\u1ec7n nh\\u00e9!<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n <li>- Collins - Grammar for IELTS<\\/li>\\r\\n <li>- Collins - Vocabulary for IELTS<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"}]', '[{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"result\":\"\",\"suggest\":\"\"},{\"from\":\"\",\"to\":\"\",\"