(474, 13, 3, 2, '{\"245\":\"Good morning. I am glad to be here for this interview. \\r\\n\\r\\nFirst, let me introduce myself. My name is Hieu and I am 22 years old. I am from Hai Duong province.My Family have 4 peoples : my parent, my sister and i. My young sister are 12 year old. She is still in secondary school. She in 6th grade. My family love me Of course, I also love them so much. I wish them always happy.\\r\\n\\r\\nMy father is working in the communication office and My mother is working in the culture office. My parents have been married for 23 years. \\r\\n\\r\\nI was born Thanh mien Town, Hai Duong province. I studied at local schools when I was a student at primary school and secondary school. Then I moved to city to follow my high-school study and started living on my own.\\r\\nNow, I am a 5th year student of Faculty of Electronics and Telecommunication , in Hanoi University of Technology.I will graduate in June , 2011.\\r\\nAt University, I am a member of Deverlopment Group about IMS, to conducted by Doctor Nguyen tai Hung , teacher of FET.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nAs for hobby, I like football and Ballad music. When alone , I often listen music of Trinh Cong Son, LeHieu or DamVinhHung. My favourite football club is Manchester United , and my icon is Sir AlexFerguson, he is really talent manager.\\r\\nI want to be an coder or network administrator in the future. \\r\\n\",\"246\":\"Good morning. I am glad to be here for this interview. \\r\\n\\r\\nFirst, let me introduce myself. My name is Hieu and I am 22 years old. I am from Hai Duong province.My Family have 4 people : my parents, my sister and me. My young sister is 12 year old. She is still in secondary school. She in 6th grade. My family love me Of course, I also love them so much. I wish them always happy.\\r\\n\\r\\nMy father is working in the communication office and My mother is working in the culture office. My parents have been married for 23 years. \\r\\n\\r\\nI was born Thanh mien Town, Hai Duong province. I studied at local schools when I was a student at primary school and secondary school. Then I moved to city to follow my high-school study and started living on my own.\\r\\nNow, I am a 5th year student of Faculty of Electronics and Telecommunication , in Hanoi University of Technology.I will graduate in June , 2011.\\r\\nAt University, I am a member of Deverlopment Group about IMS, to conducted by Doctor Nguyen tai Hung , teacher of FET.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nAs for hobby, I like football and Ballad music. When  , I often listen music of Trinh Cong Son, LeHieu or DamVinhHung. My favourite football club is Manchester United , and my icon is Sir AlexFerguson, he is really talent manager.\\r\\nI want to be an coders or network administrator on the future. \\r\\n\"}', 14, 1560914317, 1560914317, '{\"245\":{\"score\":\"0\",\"coefficient\":\"1\",\"review\":\"<p>Good morning. I am glad to be here for this interview. First, let me introduce myself. My name is Hieu and I am 22 years old. I am from Hai Duong province.My Family have 4 <span style=\\\"background-color:#FFD700;\\\">peoples<\\/span>\\u00a0(People): my parent, my sister and i. My young sister <span style=\\\"background-color:#FFD700;\\\">is (are)<\\/span><span style=\\\"color:#FF0000;\\\">\\u00a0<\\/span>12 year old. She is still in secondary school. She in 6th grade. My family love me Of course, I also love them so much. I wish them always happy. My father is working in the communication office and My mother is working in the culture office. My parents have been married for 23 years. I was born Thanh mien Town, Hai Duong province.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>I studied at local schools when I was a student at primary school and secondary school. Then I moved to city to follow my high-school study and started living on my own. Now, I am a 5th year student of Faculty of Electronics and Telecommunication , in Hanoi University of Technology.I will graduate in June , 2011. At University, I am a member of Deverlopment Group about IMS, to conducted by Doctor Nguyen tai Hung , teacher of FET. As for hobby, I like football and Ballad music. When alone , I often listen music of Trinh Cong Son, LeHieu or DamVinhHung. My favourite football club is Manchester United , and my icon is Sir AlexFerguson, he is really talent manager. I want to be an coder or network administrator in the future.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>L\\u1eddi nh\\u1eadn x\\u00e9t gi\\u00e1o vi\\u00ean: <\\/strong>B\\u1ea1n n\\u00ean h\\u1ecdc l\\u1ea1i kh\\u00f3a ng\\u1eef ph\\u00e1p c\\u0103n b\\u1ea3n tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc khi vi\\u1ebft WRiting<\\/p>\\r\\n\"},\"246\":{\"score\":\"2.5\",\"coefficient\":\"2\",\"review\":\"<p>Good morning. <span style=\\\"background-color:#FFD700;\\\">I am glad<\\/span>\\u00a0(L\\u1ed7i ng\\u1eef ph\\u00e1p) to be here for this interview. First, let me introduce myself. My name is Hieu and I am 22 years old. I am from Hai Duong province.My Family have 4 people : my parents, my sister and me. My young sister is 12 year old. She is still in secondary school. She in 6th grade. My family love me Of course, I also love them so much. I wish them always happy. My father is working in the communication office and My mother is working in the culture office. My parents have been married for 23 years. I was born Thanh mien Town, Hai Duong province. I studied at local schools when I was a student at primary school and secondary school. Then I moved to city to follow my high-school study and started living on my own. Now, I am a 5th year <span style=\\\"background-color:#FFD700;\\\">student of Faculty (Falcuty)\\u00a0<\\/span>of Electronics and Telecommunication , in Hanoi University of Technology.I will graduate in June , 2011. At University, I am a member of Deverlopment Group about IMS, to conducted by Doctor Nguyen tai Hung , teacher of FET. As for hobby, I like football and Ballad music. When , I often listen music of Trinh Cong Son, LeHieu or DamVinhHung. My favourite football club is Manchester United , and my icon is Sir AlexFerguson, he is really talent manager. I want to be an coders or network administrator on the future.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><strong>Nh\\u1eadn x\\u00e9t t\\u1eeb gi\\u00e1o vi\\u00ean:<\\/strong> C\\u1ed1 g\\u1eafng l\\u00e0m b\\u00e0i t\\u1ed1t l\\u1ea7n sau nh\\u00e9. E tham kh\\u1ea3o g\\u1ee3i \\u00fd nh\\u01b0 sau:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><img alt=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.aland.edu.vn\\/uploads\\/images\\/userfiles\\/complete_ielts_band_4_0_alandielts.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 262px; height: 369px;\\\"><\\/p>\\r\\n\"}}', NULL, 2, NULL, '{\"fullname\":\"Nguyen Thi Giang\",\"email\":\"giang.nguyen@imap.edu.vn\",\"phone\":\"977643316\",\"address\":\"H\\u00e0 N\\u1ed9i\"}'),
