(121, '<p><strong>A. </strong>the huge number of individual insects in the world</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>B. </strong>the variety of substances insects have developed to protect themselves</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>C.</strong> the potential to extract and make use of insects\' genetic codes</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>D. </strong>the similarities between different species of insect</p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>E. </strong>the manageable size of most insects</p>\r\n', 199, 2, '[\"...\",\"...\"]', 2, '[\"A\",\"B\",\"C\",\"D\",\"E\"]', 'null'),
